snippet.title: New Character Demo - "Xinyan: Aw Yeah, Rock On!" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
The pillars onstage, the stage floor, the ovations and screams of the audience, and the sparks and
 explosions from her Vision are all crucial elements that bring Xinyan's performances to life.
"Whatever's going on over there... Looks pretty rock 'n' roll to me!"
